실행 명령:
```bash
# 주석: dim32 generic baseline best checkpoint 위에서 MC-G105 finetune을 수행한다.
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=0 accelerate launch tools/train.py \
  --config configs/finetune/Denoise/svfocusdenoise_mc_g105_v1.yaml \
  --data_config configs/data/denoise_mc_g105_v1.yaml
```

